PrecisOrder fixing MONDAY, JULY 31, 1995 as the day upon which paragraph 660.2(2)(c) of the Canada Shipping Act, as enacted by section 6 of this Act, shall COME INTO FORCE, and fixing TUESDAY, AUGUST 15, 1995, as the day upon which a number of other provisions dealing with ships and oil handling facilities, shall COME INTO FORCE.
